{"tid":977210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【後悔去PSG】尼馬曾5次致電巴塞想歸隊","createTime":"2019-01-11T04:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T10:38:17.000Z","uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b60e1dbe1d8768c58d436c09e0af1e8bec6e21","tid":977210,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:32:40.000Z","msg":"　西班牙媒體《馬卡報》援引《世界體育報》的消息，尼馬對於轉會巴黎聖日耳門感到後悔，曾五次致電巴塞，希望能夠重返魯營球場。<br />\n<br />\n媒體截圖<br />\n<br />\n　　該報透露，尼馬渴望重返巴塞，他的經理人也是他的父親出面，直接跟巴塞主席貝圖美奧對話，希望能將尼馬帶回巴塞。《世界體育報》曝光了尼馬父親對貝圖美奧的那段話：「他很失望，他感到很抱歉。」<br />\n<br />\n　　據悉，尼馬相信巴黎聖日耳門缺少競技體育計劃。尼馬於2017年夏天離開巴塞，以2.22億歐元的高價加盟巴黎聖日耳門。"},{"pid":"bec70aa9fa73af48dbb1e334ac881823feac9613","tid":977210,"uid":15830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"條路自己揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ed27f02289131690ce284e0c61e18d166ccdd0","tid":977210,"uid":44277,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:45:51.000Z","msg":"碌返去囉"},{"pid":"6cb59b43a3ffb9bc9fb5ec8a18f441d607531d01","tid":977210,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"依條垃圾唔知自己有幾多斤兩"},{"pid":"03147631ca6e7c240579618010725f0f0580ad58","tid":977210,"uid":173852,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6cb59b43a3ffb9bc9fb5ec8a18f441d607531d01","tid":977210,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:41:56.000Z","msg":"依條垃圾唔知自己有幾多斤兩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:43:54.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br